NAME
    Xymon::Server - Xymon Server Interface

SYNOPSIS
      use Xymon::Server;

      my $server = Xymon::Server->({ HOME => '/home/hobbit/server' });

      print $server->hobbitserver->{BBPORT};

DESCRIPTION
    Provides a base interface for retriving configuration variables from the
    hobbit server (taken from hobbitserver.cfg).

METHODS
    Xymon::Server->hobbitserver();

    Returns a hash of configuration items from hobbitserver.cfg;

